  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/9b7340b23e7b3e664f51ebf890e5ef2e.avif?t=1727983405\" width=618 height=146 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/f531539e3139b17ecd25b12483126eee.poster.avif?t=1727983405\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/f531539e3139b17ecd25b12483126eee.webm?t=1727983405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose 1 of 5 main characters, each equipped with their own unique abilities and skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who will help you defeat the evil hordes?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Elph? The Cone Dog? Or the Barbarian?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/d44d0fdf8ceef70ae30aca9219392b16.avif?t=1727983405\" width=618 height=147 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/1fcb4a2c970aa060885e0efbb1420f62.poster.avif?t=1727983405\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/1fcb4a2c970aa060885e0efbb1420f62.webm?t=1727983405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/1fcb4a2c970aa060885e0efbb1420f62.mp4?t=1727983405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong>7 primary</strong> weapons, and <strong>12 secondary</strong> weapons - things will start to get hectic, real quick. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wand, a spear, a bow and a boomerang will make you mow smoothly through thousands of enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test and experiment to find the perfect combination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies beware!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/79e465ba6936f202de2089d48772c672.avif?t=1727983405\" width=618 height=146 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/84f3cab08cf6a07dc09db28b8a48066b.poster.avif?t=1727983405\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/84f3cab08cf6a07dc09db28b8a48066b.webm?t=1727983405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/84f3cab08cf6a07dc09db28b8a48066b.mp4?t=1727983405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Early in the game you will stumble upon a <strong>caged pet</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They’re surprisingly powerful Allies in your fight with hordes of foes! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plus, they're pretty darn cute.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/6aff94985e45371e4a835973ec40673a.avif?t=1727983405\" width=618 height=146 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/b5b4a38d0ec2a93ab3e4a77be0344047.poster.avif?t=1727983405\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/b5b4a38d0ec2a93ab3e4a77be0344047.webm?t=1727983405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/b5b4a38d0ec2a93ab3e4a77be0344047.mp4?t=1727983405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock boosts with the currency you gain during every run to make your Character stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Temporary boosts</strong> stay with you for the run, perks unlocked in the <strong>perk store</strong> help you get farther in the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And if you'd like to try something new, you can always <strong>refund and shuffle</strong> your boosts as you wish!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/22048872cc5474f0bd431ab98a81297b.avif?t=1727983405\" width=618 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play the same Story</strong> in async multiplayer <strong>with your friends</strong> and vote on how the Story evolves at the end of each Chapter! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are over 50 Plot Twists to throw in the mix, you'll find something different each run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Twists</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When playing together with friends, each of you can play through every Chapter solo, and then <strong>place your votes</strong> for Plot Twists at the end. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the voting ends, a Plot Twist is chosen and takes effect for ALL players in the Story!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/9b7340b23e7b3e664f51ebf890e5ef2e.avif?t=1727983405\" width=618 height=146 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/f531539e3139b17ecd25b12483126eee.poster.avif?t=1727983405\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/f531539e3139b17ecd25b12483126eee.webm?t=1727983405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose 1 of 5 main characters, each equipped with their own unique abilities and skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who will help you defeat the evil hordes?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Elph? The Cone Dog? Or the Barbarian?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/d44d0fdf8ceef70ae30aca9219392b16.avif?t=1727983405\" width=618 height=147 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/1fcb4a2c970aa060885e0efbb1420f62.poster.avif?t=1727983405\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/1fcb4a2c970aa060885e0efbb1420f62.webm?t=1727983405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/1fcb4a2c970aa060885e0efbb1420f62.mp4?t=1727983405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\