ss=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/b5b4a38d0ec2a93ab3e4a77be0344047.poster.avif?t=1727983405\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/b5b4a38d0ec2a93ab3e4a77be0344047.webm?t=1727983405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/b5b4a38d0ec2a93ab3e4a77be0344047.mp4?t=1727983405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock boosts with the currency you gain during every run to make your Character stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Temporary boosts</strong> stay with you for the run, perks unlocked in the <strong>perk store</strong> help you get farther in the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And if you'd like to try something new, you can always <strong>refund and shuffle</strong> your boosts as you wish!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1619420/extras/22048872cc5474f0bd431ab98a81297b.avif?t=1727983405\" width=618 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play the same Story</strong> in async multiplayer <strong>with your friends</strong> and vote on how the Story evolves at the end of each Chapter! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are over 50 Plot Twists to throw in the mix, you'll find something different each run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Twists</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When playing together with friends, each of you can play through every Chapter solo, and then <strong>place your votes</strong> for Plot Twists at the end. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the voting ends, a Plot Twist is chosen and takes effect for ALL players in the Story!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
